<br>
5 second pet &gt; all<br>
<br>
It's definitely on my &quot;List of things to get&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=falkahnhan>Falkahnhan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#333333>(12/20/02 4:24:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=481.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~nanosphere/hosicon_flag.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: QS3 worth it?</span><hr size=1> Is 5sec pets the fastest you can get?  Or does QS3 stack with spell casting haste items and Spell Casting Deftness?<br>
<br>
Falkahnhan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cydmab>Cydmab</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 695<br> <font color=#333333>(12/20/02 8:52:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=481.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: QS3 worth it?</span><hr size=1> *SPELL CASTING DEFTNESS DOES NOT EFFECT SUMMONS OR HEALS* do NOT get this worthless ability<br>
<br>
